{"tid":1760352,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［cls] 家長群里怒罵「動不動讓家長做作業，你幫我交學費啊！」被拘10天","createTime":"2019-11-28T06:55:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T07:47:25.000Z","uid":184726,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7a938f5b86113d69a2835f1bd1b61376f1a33c25","tid":1760352,"uid":184726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:55:29.000Z","msg":"轉自品蔥：<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/9802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpincong.rocks%2Farticle%2F9802&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtIGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=5197d5d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pincong.rocks/article/9802</a><br />\n<br />\n11月18日，廣東省中山市三角鎮中心小學三（2）班家長群里兩段聊天記錄在微信上傳開了。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，是因為一名學生的家長在家長群里用語音罵英語老師，表示對老師佈置作業的行為不滿。在其他家長勸說時，這位家長還說：「你們都有話不敢說話，我有話就直說！」<br />\n<br />\n從網上流傳的視頻中可以看出，由於老師佈置了線上英語作業，要求家長配合學生完成。但該家長表示自己不懂英語，無法監督女兒做英語作業。<br />\n<br />\n該家長在群里發了一連串的語音表示對英語老師的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n隨後警方稱，該家長已被依法行政拘留10日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_5067620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thepaper.cn%2FnewsDetail_forward_5067620&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtIGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=f247fff1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_5067620</a>"},{"pid":"bca16df30fba3ec9a76d6acebbd2badf0e4baab9","tid":1760352,"uid":184726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:57:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c464703bb2ecca1505869000aef2d6a6a60ba4c","tid":1760352,"uid":80503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:58:19.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"52db10452315304332f08e5d00dac8a92f147bc9","tid":1760352,"uid":189484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T07:11:25.000Z","msg":"Block"},{"pid":"cd583f1de32192a50f35fbd47e7bd41e0c58bb0b","tid":1760352,"uid":184726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52db10452315304332f08e5d00dac8a92f147bc9","tid":1760352,"uid":189484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T07:11:25.000Z","msg":"Block"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T07:47:25.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}